d\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Scottish Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Scottish League Cup|League Cup]]\n\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Scottish First Division|2008\u201309]]||[[Dundee F.C.]]||[[Scottish First Division|First Division]]||26||1||1||0||0||0||27||1\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Canada\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Canadian Championship|Voyageurs Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2009 United Soccer Leagues|2009]]||rowspan=\"2\"|Vancouver Whitecaps||First Division|| || || || ||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014|| ||\n|-\n|[[USSF Division 2 Professional League|2010]]||USSF Division 2|| || || || ||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014|| ||\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Norway\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Norwegian Football Cup|Norwegian Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2010 Norwegian Premier League|2010]]||rowspan=\"3\"|[[FK Haugesund|Haugesund]]||rowspan=\"3\"|[[Norwegian Premier League|Tippeligaen]]||28||1||4||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||32||1\n|-\n|[[2011 Norwegian Premier League|2011]]||25||1||3||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||28||1\n|-\n|[[2012 Norwegian Premier League|2012]]||1||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||2||0\n|-\n|[[2012 Norwegian First Division|2012]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Bryne FK|Bryne]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Adeccoligaen]]||8||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||8||0\n|-\n!rowspan=5| Country !!colspan=2| Canada\n!71||1||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||73||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Sweden\n!45||1|| || ||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||45||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Norway\n!109||11||9||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||118||12\n|-\n!colspan=2|United States\n!4||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||4||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Scotland\n!26||1||1||0||0||0||27||1\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Career total\n!255||14||12||1||0||0||267||15\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110605070210/http://www.canadasoccer.com/players/profile.asp?playerid=24&gender=male Player profile] \u2013 CanadaSoccer\n*{{NFT player|pid=1272}}\n*[ht